    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, it drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
